<p>The sample reflective correlation is equivalent to <a href=3D"https://en=
.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cosine_similarity" title=3D"Cosine similarity">cosine s=
imilarity</a>:
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
s=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyl=
e rr_{xy}=3D{\frac {\sum x_{i}y_{i}}{\sqrt {(\sum x_{i}^{2})(\sum y_{i}^{2}=
)}}}.}">
